aria-dropeffect.type: link / none / copy / move / execute / popup

aria-relevant.type:
type ONLY_FOR_FORMAT =
  | "text"
  | "all"
  | "additions"
  | "additions removals"
  | "additions text"
  | "removals"
  | "removals additions"
  | "removals text"
  | "text additions"
  | "text removals"

in.description: Show the component; triggers when enter or exit states
in.description_zh: 显示组件;在 ENTER 或 EXIT 状态时触发

unmountOnExit.description: If `true`, the element will unmount when `in={false}` and animation is done
unmountOnExit.description_zh: 如果为 'true'，则元素将在 'in={false}' 时卸载，并且动画完成
